_sText:
This is map is sort of a deathrun map. You start inside a cave.
You get teleported, and start playing. 
There are 4 terorist spawns for this map.
Terorist have to kill you before you reach them.
When you get to the finish, you get shotgun to kill terorist.
There is a background music, you have to press the button for music to start.
Hope you enjoy it. :)
